    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>和朋友一起召唤克苏鲁！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/09f97ba84b70752408bfe7e3ecefa6c3.poster.avif?t=1772220289\" width=472 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/09f97ba84b70752408bfe7e3ecefa6c3.webm?t=1772220289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/09f97ba84b70752408bfe7e3ecefa6c3.mp4?t=1772220289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Ritual Party》是一款合作派对游戏，你将与朋友一起进行仪式，召唤克苏鲁神话中的各种宇宙恐怖存在。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/4e6f21323a174e9199eb0d15db15f01e.poster.avif?t=1772220289\" width=472 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/4e6f21323a174e9199eb0d15db15f01e.webm?t=1772220289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/4e6f21323a174e9199eb0d15db15f01e.mp4?t=1772220289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>很多事情都会出错。有人可能会在血迹上滑倒，被触手怪卷走，或跌入冰冷的水中。来自彼岸的灵体也会制造混乱！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与此同时，你还必须在警察步步逼近、刺骨寒风席卷仪式现场的情况下，应对这一切。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/34355cff7ef84dd13cf9fccd26d342ca.poster.avif?t=1772220289\" width=472 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/34355cff7ef84dd13cf9fccd26d342ca.webm?t=1772220289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140720/extras/34355cff7ef84dd13cf9fccd26d342ca.mp4?t=1772220289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你将探索多个诡异而超现实的地点，这些场景灵感源自洛夫克拉夫特的克苏鲁神话，在那里，宇宙级的恐惧与远古谜团将挑战你对现实的认知。</strong></p>",
